# ecdsafail_skills — ignore re-fetchable downloaded research artifacts.
#
# The literature INDEX is kept in git (research/index.json, research/candidates.json,
# research/search_plan.json, research/search_results/, research/README.md). The actual
# PDFs/HTML are NOT committed — they are re-downloadable from the URLs in index.json.
# See <skill>/research/README.md for the download.py one-liner.

# Downloaded papers directory under any skill's research/ folder
**/research/papers/

# Belt-and-suspenders: any stray downloaded docs anywhere under a research/ folder
**/research/**/*.pdf
**/research/**/*.html
**/research/**/_download.log

# macOS cruft
.DS_Store
peak-qubit-reduction-workspace/
